  <header>
    
          <ol vocab="http://schema.org/" typeof="BreadcrumbList" class="breadcrumbs clearfix"><li property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem"><a property="item" typeof="WebPage" href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news"><span property="name">News</span></a></li><li property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem"><a property="item" typeof="WebPage" href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk"><span property="name">UK</span></a></li><li property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem"><a property="item" typeof="WebPage" href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics"><span property="name">UK Politics</span></a></li></ol>    
    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" ">Britons suffer &#039;historical amnesia&#039; over atrocities of their former empire, says author</h1>

    
            <div class="intro">
                <p>'Britain came to one of the richest countries in the world in the 18th century and reduced it, after two centuries of plunder, to one of the poorest'</p>
      </div>
            <ul class="caption meta inline-pipes-list">
              <li class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name"><a href="/author/matt-broomfield" title="Matt Broomfield" itemprop="sameAs">Matt Broomfield</a></span>
                  </li>
                    <li>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtagbroom">@hashtagbroom</a>
        </li>
                    <li title="5 March 2017 13:14 London"><time data-microtimes='{"published":"1488707400000","display":0,"changed":"1488719641000"}' datetime="Sun, 03/05/2017 - 13:14" unixtime="1488719641000">Sunday 5 March 2017 13:14 GMT</time></li>
                    <li class="comments">
          <a href="#commentsDiv" id="comment-count" class="icon-comment"></a>
        </li>
          </ul>
    <div id="gigya-share-btns-1"></div>
        <div class="fb-like">
      <iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Findypolitics%2F&width=450&layout=button&action=like&size=large&show_faces=false&share=false&height=35&appId=235586169789578" width="70" height="35" style="border:none;overflow:hidden;float:left;" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
      <div class="fb-info">Click to follow<br />Indy Politics</div>
